trans-unit.source: Defines an abstract base class for composable part definitions, which describe and enable the creation of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en abstrakt basisklasse etter komponerbar del definisjoner som beskriver og Aktiver opprettelse av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of a part that the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av en del av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> beskriver.

trans-unit.source: Derived types that override this method should return a new instance of a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> object every time that the method is invoked and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Avledede typer som overstyrer denne metoden skal returnere en ny forekomst av en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objektet hver gang metoden aktiveres og skal ikke returnere `null`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the objects exported by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> objekter som beskriver objektene eksportert ved del er definert av dette <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Overstyringer for denne egenskapen skal ikke returnere `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not provide exported objects, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>objekter som ble opprettet av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>ikke oppgi eksporterte objekter, returneres en tom <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601>samling i stedet.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the exported objects provided by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En samling av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ExportDefinition"> </xref> objekter som beskriver eksporterte objektene fra <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objekter som ble opprettet av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by the part defined by this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> objekter som beskriver importerer kreves av del er definert av dette <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Overstyringer for denne egenskapen skal ikke returnere `null`.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart> objects created by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> do not have imports, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> collection instead.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"></xref> objects that describe the imports required by <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"></xref> objects created by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En samling av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ImportDefinition"> </xref> objekter som beskriver importerer kreves av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePart"> </xref> objekter som ble opprettet av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the metadata for this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling med metadataene for dette <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Overrides of this property should return a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object with a case-sensitive, non-linguistic comparer, such as <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, and should never return `null`.
trans-unit.target: Overstyringer for denne egenskapen skal returnere en skrivebeskyttet <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>objekt med en små og store bokstaver, ikke linguistic sammenligningsfunksjon som <xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A>, og skal ikke returnere `null`.</xref:System.StringComparer.Ordinal%2A> </xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition> does not contain metadata, return an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object instead.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>ikke inneholder metadata, returneres en tom <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>objekt i stedet.</xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition>

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the metadata for the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En samling som inneholder metadataene for den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty, read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> object.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom skrivebeskyttet <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602> objektet.
